\v 1 \f + \fr 6:1 \ft \xt Leviticus 6:1–30 \ft in the English Bible is 5:20–6:23 in the Hebrew Bible \f* Then\f + \fr 6:1 \ft Or “And” \f* Yahweh spoke to Moses, saying, 
